from collections import defaultdict
MOD = 1000000008

def count_warp_routes(N, s, t):
    dic = defaultdict(int)
    dic[s[0]] = 1
    for (cs, ct) in zip(s[1:N - 1], t[1:N - 1]):
        dic[cs] += dic[ct]
        dic[cs] %= MOD
    return dic[t[-1]]
